===专业评价===
{{Expand section}}
与《神奇四侠》相比，续集所获得的评价要稍好一点。根据[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]]上收集的166篇评论文章，獲得37%不高的鮮度，平均得分4.8（最高10分）<ref name="RT">{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fantastic_four_2_rise_of_the_silver_surfer/|title=Fantastic Four: Rise of the Silver Surfer - Rotten Tomatoes|publisher=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=2013-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130822110120/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fantastic_four_2_rise_of_the_silver_surfer/|archive-date=2013-08-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fantastic_four/ | title=Fantastic Four | publisher=Rotten Tomatoes | accessdate=2013-07-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140904223653/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fantastic_four/ | archive-date=2014-09-04 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。而[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上通过收集的33篇评论文章给影片打出了45分（满分100），其中9篇好评，6篇差评，18篇褒贬不一<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/4-rise-of-the-silver-surfer|title=Fantastic Four: Rise of the Silver Surfer Reviews, Ratings, Credits, and More - Metacritic|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=2013-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130405225841/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/4-rise-of-the-silver-surfer|archive-date=2013-04-05|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/fantastic-four | title=Fantastic Four | publisher=Metacritic | accessdate=2013-07-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130416013011/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/fantastic-four | archive-date=2013-04-16 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。烂蕃茄上的共识评价认为《神奇四侠2》与前作相比有所进步，但仍然只是一部不成熟的简单电影，唯一的看点就是其特技效果<ref name="RT"/>。

===奖项和提名===
《神奇四侠2》获得了两座奖项，一為2008年金拖车奖最佳预告海报奖<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.goldentrailer.com/awards.gta9.php |title=9th Annual Golden Trailer Award Winner and Nominees |accessdate=2013-07-13 |publisher=Golden Trailer Awards |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100531070941/http://www.goldentrailer.com/awards.gta9.php |archivedate=2010-05-31 }}</ref>，二為洁西卡·艾巴赢得的2008年[[儿童选择奖|儿童选择奖]]“最爱电影女明星”奖<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.upi.com/Entertainment_News/2008/03/30/Cyrus-dominates-Kids-Choice-Awards/UPI-22901206900342/|title=Cyrus dominates Kids Choice Awards|accessdate=2013-07-13|publisher=UPI|date=2008-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130712190327/http://www.upi.com/Entertainment_News/2008/03/30/Cyrus-dominates-Kids-Choice-Awards/UPI-22901206900342/|archive-date=2013-07-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另外影片还获得了8项[[青少年选择奖|青少年选择奖]]提名、[[土星奖|土星奖]][[土星獎最佳科幻電影|最佳科幻片奖]]提名、一项[[MTV电影大奖|MTV电影大奖]]提名和一项{{link-en|英国国家电影奖|National Movie Awards}}提名，还被提名[[金酸莓奖|金酸莓奖]][[金酸莓獎最差女主角|最差女演员]]（洁西卡·艾巴）和最差银幕情侣（艾巴和艾恩·古福特），不过都没有得奖<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0486576/awards |title=4 Rise of the Silver Surfer (2007) - Awards |work=IMDb |accessdate=2013-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121113003815/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0486576/awards |archive-date=2012-11-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

