==重启==
{{main|驚奇4超人 (2015年電影)}}

2007年，有消息來源指出，即使《神奇四俠：銀魔現身》票房不理想，[[二十世紀福斯|二十世紀福斯]]仍在籌備一部銀色衝浪手的後續作品，並考慮製作另一部《驚奇四超人》續集，不過都還沒有投入劇本開發<ref>{{cite news|author=Galloway, Steven |title=Studios are hunting the next big property |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2007-07-10 |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3if727c623f03c782b8ad564866c828796 |access-date=2007-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071012001630/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3if727c623f03c782b8ad564866c828796 |archive-date=2007-10-12 |url-status=dead }}</ref>。2009年8月，福斯开始重启《神奇四侠》系列电影。[[阿齐瓦·高斯曼|阿齐瓦·高斯曼]]被请来出任制片人，迈克尔·格林（{{lang|en|Michael Green}}）出任编剧<ref>{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2009/film/news/fox-sets-fantastic-reboot-1118007959/ |title=Fox sets 'Fantastic' Reboot: Akiva Goldsman has been set as producer |work=Variety |date=2009-08-31 |accessdate=2013-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130630094528/http://variety.com/2009/film/news/fox-sets-fantastic-reboot-1118007959/ |archive-date=2013-06-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.superherohype.com/features/articles/99367-fox-is-rebooting-fantastic-four|title= Fox is Rebooting Fantastic Four |work= Superherohype |date= 2009-08-31|accessdate= 2013-07-13|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130613154752/http://www.superherohype.com/features/articles/99367-fox-is-rebooting-fantastic-four|archive-date= 2013-06-13|dead-url= no}}</ref>。2012年7月中旬，公司正式宣布将请因《[[超能失控|超能失控]]》而成名的[[乔什·特兰克|乔什·特兰克]]担任导演<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/171669-comic-con-fantastic-four-director-confirmed-while-daredevil-director-exits|title= Comic-Con: Fantastic Four Director Confirmed While Daredevil Director Exits|date= 2012-07-11|accessdate= 2013-07-13|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130607094841/http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/171669-comic-con-fantastic-four-director-confirmed-while-daredevil-director-exits|archive-date= 2013-06-07|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.deadline.com/2012/07/comic-con-fox-sets-fantastic-four-and-daredevil-reboots-and-puts-joe-cornish-on-rust-loses-david-slade-on-daredevil-redo/ |title= Comic-Con: Fox Sets Reboots Of ‘Fantastic Four’ |date= 2012-07-11 |accessdate= 2012-03-19 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120906064120/http://www.deadline.com/2012/07/comic-con-fox-sets-fantastic-four-and-daredevil-reboots-and-puts-joe-cornish-on-rust-loses-david-slade-on-daredevil-redo/ |archive-date= 2012-09-06 |dead-url= no }}</ref>，杰里米·斯莱特（{{lang|en|Jeremy Slater}}）出任编剧<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/171731-comic-con-fantastic-four-reboot-gets-a-writer |title=Comic-Con: Fantastic Four Reboot Gets a Writer |date=2012-07-13 |accessdate=2013-07-13 |author=Perry, Spencer |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511070000/http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/171731-comic-con-fantastic-four-reboot-gets-a-writer |archive-date=2013-05-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年2月[[马修·沃恩|马修·沃恩]]成为电影的制片人<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/175179-matthew-vaughn-to-produce-fantastic-four |title=Matthew Vaughn to Produce Fantastic Four |date=2013-02-22 |accessdate=2013-07-13 |author=Lesnick, Silas |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130706101841/http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/175179-matthew-vaughn-to-produce-fantastic-four |archive-date=2013-07-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年6月，[[赛斯·葛雷恩·史密斯|赛斯·葛雷恩·史密斯]]被请来为电影的剧本润色<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/175237-seth-grahame-smith-boards-fantastic-four|title=Seth Grahame-Smith Boards Fantastic Four|date=2013-02-26|accessdate=2013-07-13|author=Lesnick, Silas|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130613183933/http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/175237-seth-grahame-smith-boards-fantastic-four|archive-date=2013-06-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。电影于2014年5月初开拍，8月下旬完工<ref name="Collider">{{Cite web |url=http://collider.com/the-fantastic-four-movie-details-josh-trank/ |title='The Fantastic Four' Movie Details, Images, Easter Eggs, Tone, and More |last=Weintaub |first=Steve |date=2015-01-27 |website=Collider |access-date=2015-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150127102947/http://collider.com/the-fantastic-four-movie-details-josh-trank/ |archive-date=2015-01-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nola.com/movies/index.ssf/2014/05/fantastic_four_reboot_begins_f.html |title='Fantastic Four' reboot begins filming today in Baton Rouge; here's what we know so far |last=Scott |first=Mike |date=2014-05-05 |website=Times-Picayune |access-date=2014-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140505200843/http://www.nola.com/movies/index.ssf/2014/05/fantastic_four_reboot_begins_f.html |archive-date=2014-05-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2014/05/05/fantastic-four-begins-filming-in-louisiana/ |title=‘Fantastic Four’ begins filming in Louisiana! |last=Christine |date=2014-05-05 |publisher=onlocationvacations.com |access-date=2014-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140506134812/http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2014/05/05/fantastic-four-begins-filming-in-louisiana/ |archive-date=2014-05-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://uproxx.com/gammasquad/2014/08/fantastic-four-the-thing-first-look/ |title=Fantastic Four Director Josh Trank Tweets a First Look At The Thing |last=Panda |first=Robo |date=2014-08-23 |publisher=Uproxx |access-date=2014-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826131107/http://uproxx.com/gammasquad/2014/08/fantastic-four-the-thing-first-look/ |archive-date=2014-08-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影片獨立於[[漫威电影宇宙|漫威电影宇宙]]之外<ref>{{cite web |work = Variety|first=Michael|last=Fleming |title=Fox sets 'Fantastic' reboot|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118007959?refCatId=13|date=2009-08-31|accessdate = 2011-07-26 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/60Te8IBfd?url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118007959?refCatId=13 |archivedate=2011-07-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url= https://twitter.com/mrmarkmillar/statuses/305039875068014592 | title= Twitter _ mrmarkmillar  Just off the phone with Fox |website=Twitter| accessdate= 2013-07-14 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151105062800/https://twitter.com/mrmarkmillar/statuses/305039875068014592 | archive-date= 2015-11-05 | dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comicbookmovie.com/fansites/MarvelFreshman/news/?a=75219|title=Kevin Feige Shares Thoughts On FOX's Potential Marvel Cinematic Universe|author=DCMarvelFreshman|accessdate=2013-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130307062230/http://www.comicbookmovie.com/fansites/MarvelFreshman/news/?a=75219|archive-date=2013-03-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>，于2015年8月7日在美國上映<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-preview-fantastic-four-813449 |title=Box-Office Preview: 'Fantastic Four' to Lead Jam-Packed Weekend |last=McClintock |first=Pamela |date=2015-08-05 |website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |access-date=2015-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150807082107/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-preview-fantastic-four-813449 |archive-date=2015-08-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/x-men-spin-deadpool-gets-734172?mobile_redirect=false |title='X-Men' Spin-Off 'Deadpool' Gets Winter 2016 Release Date |last=McClintock |first=Pamela |date=2014-09-18 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |access-date=2014-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140919020612/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/x-men-spinoff-deadpool-gets-734172 |archive-date=2014-09-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

